    "body": "<span class=\"solution-visible-txt\">All submissions for this problem are available.</span><p>Joey is very good friend of Ross &amp; Monica. Joey loves his<br />\nfriends so much. On the eve of New Year, They invited Joey for a party. He plans to go for party and give some beautiful flowers to everyone there in party. Unfortunately,<br />\nHe don\u2019t have enough money to buy flowers, but as today is a New Year eve, every shop is giving free roses. He<br />\ndecides to take advantage.</p>\n<p>Well, there are <b>N</b> shops on the way. Each shop will give <b>A<sub>i</sub></b> roses, but if and only if Joey didn\u2019t take any roses<br />\nfrom the shop directly before the current one. Joey wants maximum roses. He wants to know the maximum amount of<br />\nroses he can collect on his way. </p>\n<p>\u00a0</p>\n<h3>Input</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>First Line Contains Test Cases <b>T</b></li>\n<li>First Line of every test case contains an Integer <b>N</b> indicating number of shops on the way.</li>\n<li>Next Line of each test case contains <b>N</b> space separated integers <b>A<sub>0</sub></b>, <b>A<sub>1</sub></b>, <b>A<sub>2</sub></b>,.......,<b>A<sub>N-1</sub></b> , where <b>A<sub>i</sub></b> indicates amount of roses given by i<sup>th</sup> shop.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>\u00a0</p>\n<h3>Output</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Output the maximum amount of roses he can collect on his way in new line.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>\u00a0</p>\n<h3>Constraints</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><b>1</b> \u2264 <b>T</b> \u2264 <b>100</b></li>\n<li><b>1</b> \u2264 <b>N</b> \u2264 <b>10<sup>4</sup></b></li>\n<li><b>1</b> \u2264 <b>A<sub>i</sub></b> \u2264 <b>10<sup>9</sup></b></li>\n</ul>\n<p>\u00a0</p>\n<h3>Example</h3>\n<pre><b>Input:</b>\n2\n3\n2 5 2\n5\n1 4 3 1 5\n\n<b>Output:</b>\n5\n9\n</pre>",
